      "writtenOn": "2017-02-07T19:31:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would prefer that allocators are paired with their proper free-ers, so an allocation by HeapAlloc() would be freed by HeapFree(). That may actually be an argument for a base::UncheckedMallocFree().",
