      },
      "lineNbr": 43,
      "author": {
        "id": 1177549
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-07T20:55:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I envision we\u0027ll want to use this for other troublesome allocation spots, in which case you\u0027ll have to duplicate the reset()-before-alloc pattern everywhere. Your call, but the interface factors this out , as-is.",
      "parentUuid": "34e5d795_ca1741cf",
      "revId": "7f90922bda75a748794096fb4205c84e37525faf",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
